---
layout: base
title: "Speak at nullEDGE 2026 | Call for Proposals"
description: "Share your ServiceNow expertise with 1,000+ practitioners. Submit your talk for nullEDGE 2026 events."
permalink: /speakers/
---

<div class="container wrapper flow">
  {# Hero Section #}
  <section class="prose text-center">
    <span class="badge">Call for Proposals</span>
    <h1>Speak at nullEDGE 2026</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Share your ServiceNow expertise with 1,000+ practitioners worldwide. 
      No sales pitches—just real code and actual implementations.
    </p>
    
    <div class="button-group">
      <a href="#events" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary">View Events & Submit</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# Why Speak Section #}
  <section class="region flow">
    <h2 class="text-center">Why Speak at nullEDGE?</h2>
    <div class="grid-3col gap-l">
      <div class="card flow">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Reach Practitioners</h3>
        <p>Connect with 1,000+ ServiceNow developers, admins, and architects who are eager to learn from your experience.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card flow">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m15 14 5-5-5-5"/><path d="M20 9H9.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 4 14.5v0A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 9.5 20H13"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Build Your Brand</h3>
        <p>Establish yourself as a thought leader in the ServiceNow community. All sessions are recorded and promoted.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card flow">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Zero Pressure</h3>
        <p>Virtual format means no travel required. Casual, practitioner-focused environment—be yourself and share what you know.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# What We're Looking For #}
  <section class="region flow">
    <h2 class="text-center">What We're Looking For</h2>
    <div class="card flow">
      <div class="flow gap-m">
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold">Real-World Implementations</p>
            <p class="text-muted">Production code, actual architectures, and lessons learned from live systems</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold">Technical Deep Dives</p>
            <p class="text-muted">Show us the code, walk through the logic, explain the technical decisions</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold">Problem-Solving Stories</p>
            <p class="text-muted">How you solved a tough challenge, what didn't work, and what you'd do differently</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold">Community Contributions</p>
            <p class="text-muted">Open source tools, scripts, frameworks, or methodologies you've built and shared</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold">Practitioner Perspectives</p>
            <p class="text-muted">Your experience in the trenches—what works, what doesn't, and why</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="alert alert-warning">
        <p class="font-semibold">What We DON'T Want:</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted">
          Product pitches, vendor demos, sales presentations, or marketing content. 
          nullEDGE is 100% practitioner-focused—keep it technical and authentic.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# Events with CFP #}
  <section id="events" class="region flow">
    <h2 class="text-center">2026 Events Accepting Proposals</h2>
    <div class="grid-2col gap-l">
      {% for event in events2026.events %}
        {% if event.cfpUrl %}
        <div class="card flow">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="flex-between">
              <h3 class="h4">{{ event.shortName }}</h3>
              <span class="badge">CFP Available</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted">{{ event.description }}</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card-body flow gap-s">
            <div class="info-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" x2="16" y1="2" y2="6"/><line x1="8" x2="8" y1="2" y2="6"/><line x1="3" x2="21" y1="10" y2="10"/></svg>
              <span>Event: {{ event.date | formatDate("MMMM D, YYYY") }}</span>
            </div>
            
            {% if event.sessionCount %}
            <div class="info-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
              <span>{{ event.sessionCount }} Sessions</span>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            
            {% if event.cfpOpen and event.cfpClose %}
            <div class="info-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
              <span>CFP: {{ event.cfpOpen | formatDate("MMM D") }} - {{ event.cfpClose | formatDate("MMM D, YYYY") }}</span>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            
            <a href="{{ event.cfpUrl }}" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              Submit Your Talk
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  {# FAQ Section #}
  <section class="region flow">
    <h2 class="text-center">Speaker FAQ</h2>
    <div class="flow gap-m">
      <div class="card flow">
        <h3 class="h4">How long should my session be?</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">
          Most sessions are 15-30 minutes, with time for Q&A. We'll work with you to determine the best format for your content.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card flow">
        <h3 class="h4">Do I need to be an expert?</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">
          No! If you've built something interesting, solved a tough problem, or learned valuable lessons, you have something to share. Authenticity matters more than credentials.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card flow">
        <h3 class="h4">Will sessions be recorded?</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">
          Yes, all sessions are recorded and published on our YouTube channel. This helps extend your reach beyond the live event.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card flow">
        <h3 class="h4">Can I submit multiple proposals?</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">
          Absolutely! Feel free to submit multiple topics. We appreciate speakers with multiple areas of expertise.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# CTA Section #}
  <section class="region text-center">
    <div class="card flow prose">
      <h2>Ready to Share Your Knowledge?</h2>
      <p>Join 40+ speakers who presented at nullEDGE 2025. The community is waiting to learn from your experience.</p>
      <div class="button-group">
        <a href="#events" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary">Submit Your Talk</a>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-lg btn-outline">View Upcoming Events</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<style>
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border: 2px solid hsl(var(--border));
    border-radius: calc(var(--radius) - 2px);
    font-size: var(--size-step--1);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .button-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .card {
    background: hsl(var(--card));
    border: 2px solid hsl(var(--border));
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: var(--space-m-l);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: hsl(var(--primary));
    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px hsl(var(--primary) / 0.1);
  }

  .card-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    background: hsl(var(--primary) / 0.1);
    border-radius: calc(var(--radius) - 2px);
    color: hsl(var(--primary));
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card-header {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card-body {
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 2px solid hsl(var(--border));
  }

  .flex-between {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .checklist-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 0;
  }

  .checklist-item svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: hsl(var(--primary));
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .checklist-item .font-semibold {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .info-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: hsl(var(--muted-foreground));
    font-size: var(--size-step--1);
  }

  .info-item svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: hsl(var(--primary));
  }

  .alert {
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    border: 2px solid hsl(var(--border));
  }

  .alert-warning {
    background: hsl(var(--muted) / 0.5);
    border-color: hsl(var(--primary) / 0.3);
  }

  .text-muted {
    color: hsl(var(--muted-foreground));
    font-size: var(--size-step--1);
  }

  .font-semibold {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .grid-2col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(300px, 100%), 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-m);
  }

  .grid-3col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(250px, 100%), 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-m);
  }

  .gap-l {
    gap: var(--space-l);
  }

  .gap-m {
    gap: var(--space-m);
  }

  .gap-s {
    gap: var(--space-s);
  }
</style>
